The paper deals with image annotation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of priors and machine learning techniques to improve the accuracy of image annotation suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The incorporation of CNN feature vectors and word vectors for tags indicates that the paper could also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
